name:                constant
stack:               ( x -- )    ( defining word )
                     ( -- x )    ( defined word )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            stateless
category:            defining words
input stream:        one space delimited string

decription:          parses input stream for the name of a constant, creates that
                     constant and associates value x with it.

standard:            yes
                     https://forth-standard.org/standard/core/CONSTANT

